<br>
As for the question asked? Yes, epics should be changed/upgraded. At the very least, suit them all with a click-activated effect, so they will retain a measure of usefulness even after you stop wielding them as weapons. A good example of such an epic is the cleric equivalent; even on the Plane of Time, you will still be using that item because of its right click effect.<br>
